      <title>中东事件引发市场不安，欧洲天然气价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/european-gas-advances-as-middle-east-events-spark-market-jitters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲天然气价格延续上涨势头，凸显出地缘政治风险下对燃料供应的担忧加剧。]]></description>
