    <item>
      <title>香港豪宅售价比经纪人估计低 60%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/hong-kong-house-sold-for-60-less-than-market-expectations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港一座豪宅以 3.6 亿港元（4600 万美元）的价格售出，比代理商估计的价格低 60%，成为越来越多以大幅折扣交易的豪宅名单中的一员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/hong-kong-house-sold-for-60-less-than-market-expectations</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 07:16:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿达尼能源股份出售获得三倍出价，买家蜂拥而至</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/adani-energy-share-sale-gets-three-fold-bids-as-buyers-pile-in</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度亿万富翁高塔姆阿达尼 (Gautam Adani) 的输电部门收到的出价是该公司计划通过股票出售筹集资金的三倍多，这表明投资者兴趣浓厚。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/adani-energy-share-sale-gets-three-fold-bids-as-buyers-pile-in</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 07:09:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国物价上涨乏力 向欧洲央行发出混合信号</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/france-s-muted-price-pickup-offers-ecb-mixed-signals-for-region</link>
      <description><![CDATA[7月份，法国通胀率增速低于预期，在德国通胀压力加大的情况下，这给欧洲央行官员提供了好坏参半的证据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/france-s-muted-price-pickup-offers-ecb-mixed-signals-for-region</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 06:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科威特顶级伊斯兰银行考虑成立一家规模 500 亿美元的贷款机构</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/top-kuwaiti-islamic-banks-eye-deal-to-create-50-billion-lender</link>
      <description><![CDATA[科威特两家最大的伊斯兰银行正在考虑合并，创建一家资产超过 500 亿美元的区域性银行巨头。]]></description>
