      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 06:43:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲需求强劲，达能销售额超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/danone-sales-beat-forecasts-amid-strong-asia-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[达能公司 (Danone SA) 表示，由于该公司避开了竞争对手所遭受的生活成本上涨对消费者信心的影响，消费者再次开始购买价格更昂贵的品牌商品。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/danone-sales-beat-forecasts-amid-strong-asia-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 05:35:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行在美联储会议前数小时上调基准利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/boj-hikes-interest-rate-unveils-plan-to-cut-back-bond-buying</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行上调基准利率，并公布将债券购买量减半的计划，彰显其货币政策正常化的决心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/boj-hikes-interest-rate-unveils-plan-to-cut-back-bond-buying</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 03:59:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行加息开启关键一天，股市上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，日本央行将基准利率上调至 2008 年以来的最高水平，拉开了对市场至关重要的一天，全球股市随之上涨。科技股出现反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 22:44:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国市场持续疲软，欧莱雅销售增长乏力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/l-oreal-sales-growth-disappoints-as-weakness-in-china-persists</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最大的美容产品制造商欧莱雅公司 (L’Oréal SA) 公布第二季度销售增长乏力，原因是受到中国市场疲软的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/l-oreal-sales-growth-disappoints-as-weakness-in-china-persists</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 16:03:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>空客评估航天部门 首席执行官考虑所有选择</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/airbus-tktktkt-on-slower-plane-deliveries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[空中客车公司已开始对其陷入困境的航天业务进行全面审查，首席执行官纪尧姆·福里表示，他正在权衡该子公司未来的所有可能性，因为该公司上半年的支出高达 10 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/airbus-tktktkt-on-slower-plane-deliveries</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 15:52:53 GMT</pubDate>
